ipermail\/bitcoin-dev\/2023-March\/021521.html\">Ordinal swap BIP<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Lightning<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>\u26a1\ufe0f <a href=\"https:\/\/lists.linuxfoundation.org\/pipermail\/lightning-dev\/2023-March\/003886.html\">Resize channels offchain with hierarchical channels<\/a><\/li><li>\ud83e\udea1 <a href=\"https:\/\/lists.linuxfoundation.org\/pipermail\/lightning-dev\/2023-March\/003895.html\">Discussion about channel splicing spec on mailing list<\/a><ul><li>Eclair is now working in channel splicing<\/li><li>As discussed at earlier meetup, so is Core LN (Dusty\u2019s PR)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Nostr<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>\ud83e\udec2 <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/nostr-protocol\/nips\/pull\/405\">Nicolas Burtey drafts P2P trading spec NIP<\/a><\/li><li>\ud83d\udd0b <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/voltage_cloud\/status\/1646545761461497861\">Voltage launches Nostr toolkit<\/a><\/li><li>\u26a0\ufe0f <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/nostr-protocol\/nips\/pull\/457\/files\">NIP-69 &#8211; defined vocabulary for content reporting<\/a><\/li><li>\ud83d\udd11 <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/nostr-protocol\/nips\/pull\/455\">Updates to NIP-26 delegated events signing<\/a><\/li><li>\ud83d\udfe3 <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/nobu-maeda\/n3xb\">n3xb &#8211; naive nostr no-KYC exchange for bitcoin<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Regulatory &amp; Business<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>\ud83d\udc68\u200d\u2696\ufe0f <a href=\"https:\/\/www.torekeland.com\/roman-sterlingov\/\">Lawyers assisting Roman Sterlingov, accused of running Bitcoin Fog, a custodial mixer<\/a><ul><li>\ud83c\udf99\ufe0f <a href=\"https:\/\/www.podpage.com\/citadeldispatch\/cd100-the-disturbing-chainalysis-led-prosecution-of-roman-sterlingov-with-mike-hassard-and-tor-ekeland\/\">Interview with lawyers on Citadel Dispatch<\/a><\/li><li>Can faulty Chainalysis assertions result in fault imprisonment?<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>\ud83d\udcb0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bleepingcomputer.com\/news\/security\/ncr-suffers-aloha-pos-outage-after-blackcat-ransomware-attack\/\">NCR attacked by Ransomware<\/a><ul><li>\ud83d\udcc3 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.businesswire.com\/news\/home\/20230417005506\/en\/NCR-Reports-Cybersecurity-Incident\">Press release from NCR<\/a><\/li><li>\ud83d\udc08\u200d\u2b1b <a href=\"https:\/\/www.varonis.com\/blog\/blackcat-ransomware\">Analysis of BlackCat\/ALPHV gang<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>It\u2019s almost time for&nbsp;Bitcoin Socratic Seminar #17! What is a Socratic Seminar? Inspired by other BitDevs meetups around the US, our Socratic Seminar events are formatted to foster debate, information sharing and lively discussion. Discussion topics are provided ahead of the event The event moderator(s) leads the audience through the topics Raise your hand to&hellip; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/atlantabitdevs.org\/2023\/04\/18\/bitcoin-socratic-seminar-17\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Bitcoin Socratic Seminar #17<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":285,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[4],"tags":[8,14,7,25,35,38,16,42],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.5.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Bitcoin Socratic Seminar #17 - Atlanta BitDevs<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/atlantabitdevs.org\/2023\/04\/18\/bitcoin-socratic-seminar-17\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Bitcoin Socratic Seminar #17 - Atlanta BitDevs\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"It\u2019s almost time for&nbsp;Bitcoin Socratic Seminar #17! What is a Socra